text: Truly remarkable inviting home. Well situated for privacy in the picturesque Parkside neighborhood. This home has it all featuring sunlit soaring ceilings flowing around into living room which provides open living with dining & see-thru fireplace to family room joining the show stopping kitchen-floor to ceiling marble tile, quartz counters, 2 ovens, walk-in pantry. Calming primary suite offers cozy fireplace, private balcony & 5-piece ensuite w/walk-in closet. Addit 2 bdrms, full bath, laundry & large 4th bdrm or bonus rec room w/murphy bed, office & powder. French doors off the dining area to fenced patio with turf, beautiful waterfall & lush plantings. Incredible parklike outdoors, not one area left unaware. A place to come home & relax.

Imagine waking up to breathtaking bay and island views every morning from this spacious home. Big shop plus 2 car garage and artist studio for all toys and hobbies. Both levels feature cozy masonry Finnish fireplaces, creating a warm ambiance throughout. The beautiful kitchen boasts shaker-style cabinets, granite countertops, stainless appliances and an inviting eat in area with built in custom cabinets. Downstairs, unwind in the family room or relax in the sauna after a long day. Enjoy outdoor living with front and back decks, perfect for entertaining or enjoy scenery. Lots of extra parking for all sumner enjoyment! Located in the Shelter Bay community, you'll have access to amenities like a pool, new marina, beach & more. Leased land.

Private lot on Center Island, WA! Your ideal San Juan Islands retreat awaits on this peaceful, privately owned 1/2 acre lot with partial water views. Power, water, and septic installed. Whether camping under the PNW canopy or constructing your vacation home, the possibilities are endless. Electric golf carts add to the island charm. CIA amenities include deep-water docks, a clubhouse, caretakers, trails, waterfront picnic areas, wifi, sports court, mailhouse, computer room, bathrooms, shower, laundry, private airstrip, rental equipment, and limitless fun. Experience premier fishing, crabbing, shrimping, and PNW summer adventures. Just miles from Canada! Accessible by Anacortes WA water taxi, air travel, or boat. pack in, pack out.

Welcome to this well maintained 4-bedroom home, featuring wonderful layout with multiple living spaces. With main living & dining areas transition seamlessly into open kitchen w/eat-at peninsula, 2nd dining & family room. All overlooking the inviting backyard oasis, which includes flat grassy yard, mature landscaping, fruit trees, hot tub & covered deckperfect for both relaxation & entertainment. The interior boasts updates throughout. Upper level gives all bedrooms with full bath. Spacious primary suite offers walk-in closet & 5-piece en-suite. This home is ideally situated near schools, beautiful forestlands, Heart Lake & scenic Mt Erie, providing easy access to nature & outdoor activities. Exceptional property in an unbeatable location.

Welcome to your new home! This open and bright residence is move-in ready, featuring stunning granite countertops atop beautifully painted cabinets with a full tile backsplash in the kitchen. The bathrooms boast elegant marble counters, complemented by stylish paint throughout the house. Enjoy the convenience of living in Skagit Highlands, with access to multiple parks and walking trails. Located close to hospitals, schools, shopping, and all amenities, this home is perfect for a comfortable and connected lifestyle. Don't miss out on this treasure!

Brand New Community Bay View in the Burlington Country Club Area. The plan features 1888 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Kitchen Island opens to Great Room, dining area. Primary Bedroom with Large 5 piece Bath and walk-in closet upstairs with 3 other Bedrooms. Large back patio and covered front porch. Bay View schools. Close to Skagit Country Club, Edison, Bow, La Conner and Anacortes. Shopping a short distance away. Special Financing options when working with the Preferred Lender. Buyers are able to customize finishes at the Design Center. For GPS use 16850 Peterson Road.

Welcome to Anchor Cove Marina, your gateway to the San Juan Islands! This 40' open slip, with a 5' overhang and 16' width, offers easy access with side fingers and storage space. Conveniently located in Old Town Anacortes, and just a short walk to downtown amenities. The marina features 30-amp power, a security gate, and an on-site Harbormaster. Enjoy amenities like a clubhouse with showers, a picnic area, fish cleaning and crab cooking stations, and onsite laundry. There's also a workshop, a head pump-out cart, and storage for tenders, small boats, and trailers!
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Nestled on 4.6 acres of pristine FLAT land. This scenic 2337 sqft modern farmhouse boasts a harmonious balance of rural bliss & modernity, minutes from downtown w/idyllic views of the sunset kissing the surrounding mountains. The barn/shop was designed to accommodate animals or your recreational toys. Explore your green thumb in the private blueberry garden, fruit orchard & chicken coop, while utilizing 4 fenced sections thoughtfully crafted for a hobby farm. Private backyard patio was designed to entertain w/a custom fire pit & covered BBQ area. Inside, discover a spacious laundry area, office, bath & primary bed w/a spa-like full bath on the main level. Upstairs, 3 bedrooms & a full bath provide ample space for guests. Not in Flood Zone

A one of a kind home located in desirable Conway neighborhood. Over an acre and a half of landscaped property, 3 bedrooms, plus office that could be used as a bedroom, 3 bathroom home with space for entertaining. Spectacular Westerly views capturing amazing sunsets and views of the mountains and sound. Detached garage and separate workshop/storage shed. RV/Boat parking. Property backs up to miles of trails and access to Lake Sixteen. Completely remodeled in 2021 with energy efficient windows and heat/cooling pump. Half a sport court for basketball and pickleball, includes brand new hot tub spa and sauna. Property is two parcels of land, with buildable possibility. RV/tiny home hookup.

Discover the potential of this charming home in the heart of Mount Vernon. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this house is ready for a loving owner to transform it into a dream home. Look past the current state to see the endless possibilities that await. Centrally located near churches, hospitals, and just minutes from I-5 and downtown Mount Vernon, this property offers convenience and a prime location. Make this house your own and enjoy everything Mount Vernon has to offer.

Enjoy privacy, river/beach access, and mountain views on five parcels totaling 86.57 tree-lined acres with income potential! This property includes a spacious home, barn, stables, garage/shop, and more! Large 1920's farmhouse home with hardwood floors and beautiful wood wrapped windows and doors features an unfinished basement and is mid-reno and ready for your imaginative touch. Huge garage/shop with loft area above featuring wood floors. Large barn with stables, additional paddocks, hay field, and a chicken coop with water and power. Fish the Skagit River from your property. So much potential - make it your own!

Pottery Barn-inspired Craftsman gem, conveniently located near marinas, WA Park, WA State ferry, the airport, and more. This timeless single-level floorplan features a primary suite thoughtfully separated from guest bedrooms by the expansive living, kitchen, and dining areas accented by Brazilian cherry floors, vaulted ceilings, and shiplap walls. A composite deck connects the living room to the primary suite, offering seamless indoor-outdoor living. Nestled against a serene greenbelt, the sizeable backyard offers great privacy. Additional amenities include a 50-year roof, covered entry, amazing ambient light, bonus room/4th bedroom above garage, office space, RV/boat parking, exterior irrigation, landscape lighting, and a custom driveway.

Charming single-story, 2-bedroom, 1 bath home. Spacious full bathroom with storage. Remodeled kitchen cabinets and granite countertops. Ample natural light from the South with newer vinyl windows. Partially fenced yard. Detached single-car garage and shop allows for plenty of storage at 550 sq/ft. Garage sold as-is. Plenty of off-street parking located on a quiet cul-de-sac street. Many options to put your personal touch in the home. Walking distance to nearby restaurants and The Store in Anacortes, at the top of Commercial Ave.

Beautiful 3 bed/1.75 bath LEVEL ENTRY home built by Landed Gentry in desirable Montreaux 55+ community. Over 1850/sf of living space with open great room design, plus separate formal sitting room. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, built-in pantry, pull-out shelving, large island w/seating, plus dining area. Great room with upgraded gas fireplace & hardwood floors. Primary suite has private bath w/double vanity, granite counter, walk-in shower & walk-in closet. Laundry w/utility sink. Covered patio plumbed for gas BBQ. Low maintenance yard. SunSetter automatic shades on key windows. Attached two car garage upgraded to add five additional feet of space, lots of storage.

At the end of the Drive, tucked in the forest, with a creek at the back of the lot, you will love this serene 5 acre parcel. Cleared area with grass. Newer road / driveway extends back into the property by roughly 100 yards (300' Feet). This lot is part of a small community just minutes away from fishing, hiking and a multitude of outdoor activities. Bring your builder and get started on your dream home in the North Cascades.

Centrally Located 4 bedroom rambler with a panoramic view of the mountains and valley. Just a short drive away are views of Mt Baker. Property includes a 3 stall hobby stable/shop and a large patio area in the backyard. Interiors include hardwood floors, large laundry and craft room, free standing gas stove in the family room. Lots of builtins and an open kitchen/dining area. Located in a very desireable setting with just a short drive to I-5. Also plenty of room to park your RV or boat!

Lake Cavanaugh lakefront on sale! Discover the perfect retreat on the tranquil shores of Lake Cavanaugh. 61' of pristine lakefront with private dock, great beach for swimming, sunbathing & fun. Over 2000' sq. ft. of comfortable living space to welcome friends. Main floor bdrm, full bath, 2 upper level bedrooms, 3/4 bath. Recently updated deck provides an ideal space for outdoor dining, entertaining or simply enjoying in the breathtaking views. Lake Cavanaugh is a highly desirable lake known for its crystal clear water, natural beauty and serene environment. Make unforgettable memories here all year long. This is a great deal for lakefront property thats move in ready.

Experience unparalleled elegance in this island home. Courtyard w/tranquil water feature into foyer w/soaring ceilings. Living areas captivate w/wood, metal & concrete accents+whole home smart system. Chefs kitchen boasts thoughtful layout & elements, breakfast nook & dining area. Main lvl offers 1 bdrm, 2.5 bths, loft, office/guest living & storage. Primary suite w/water views, walk-in closet, w/d & luxe en-suite, soaking tub framed by picture window. French doors lead to view patio w/stone fp, dining, BBQ & steps to sports court. Addt patio provides private retreat w/fire pit. Lower lvl gives 2 bdrms w/en-suite bths & family rm. Separate 1bdrm guest dwelling. 2-bay garage w/3rd bay shop+built-ins. Enjoy community trails & beach access.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Perfectly located near Anacortes forest lands, parks, hospital, marinas, and downtown, this immaculate condo in Mariner's Ridge offers the easy life! A beautifully landscaped front entry leads to bright and open living spaces, this condo has much to offer. The kitchen has ample storage and enough counter space to please the best cook. In the primary bedroom you will find a large walk-in closet, an attached ensuite bathroom w/dual sinks, a soaker tub and a separate shower. Enjoy brand new carpeting, upgraded lighting, outdoor patio, in-unit laundry and assigned covered parking. It's a short commute to NAS Whidbey and close to Old Town Anacortes for the best shopping, dining and waterfront enjoyment. Now is a good time to call Anacortes home!

Adorable single story, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a great layout, fresh exterior paint and a new roof! Fully fenced yard with lawn and room for a garden. Covered parking and large shed. Enjoy the mornings on the covered patio. Asphalt driveway and gated entry. Walking distance to downtown Burlington with fantastic dining and shopping and just moments to I5.

Spacious home with ample shop space, parking, & beautiful mountain & valley views in a peaceful setting. This property features a 1, 707 SF house, an oversized 840 SF 2-car garage, a 24 x 35 attached shop, & a 36 x 40 detached shop with 8' & 12' doors on a 0.86 acre lot. The home offers 3 bdrms & 1.75 baths, to include a primary suite with an en-suite bath. It also provides a practical kitchen, living & dining rooms, & a large laundry/utility room, ready for you to update everything just how you want it! Outside, there's plenty of space for a garden to complement the mature fruit trees, or enjoy the ample yard for playing & entertaining. A heat pump keeps you cool and comfortable all summer! Plenty of parking for your equipment, RV, or boat!

This beautiful stick built handcrafted home features three bedrooms, two full baths, and an attached two-car garage. Its open-concept design seamlessly integrates the dining room, living room, and kitchen featuring a stylish island and solid surface white quartz countertops. Abundant storage with a pantry, laminate flooring throughout. The primary suite offers a spacious walk-in closet and a generous bathroom. Ample windows provide abundant natural light and showcase views of the Cascade Mountains. Fully fenced backyard with a patio ready for great summer BBQs. Situated within walking distance of Silo Park and downtown Concrete. Additional features include a heat pump, and no HOA fees. Come, make this charming home yours today!

This luxurious 3-bed, 2-bath home spans over 3, 200 sq ft and is flooded with natural light. The open-concept living area features a gourmet kitchen with ample counter space, cabinets, and pantry, while the main room includes a built-in office, perfect for remote work. The primary suite is a true retreat with a walk-in closet, a spa-like ensuite with a sauna, and a private balcony with serene water views. The lush outdoor space includes a 50-foot private dock, ideal for boating. The home is equipped with solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. Additional features include hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, ample storage, a 2-car attached garage, and a stair chair lift for easy access upstairs. This home perfectly blends luxury and comfort.

Turn key & adorable as can be, make this charmer yours! Located in Brickyard Creek w/3 bed, 1.75 bath, the current owners touch is evident w/tasteful updates throughout. Boasting an open concept floor plan w/vaulted ceilings, kitchen w/bar seating, cozy gas fireplace, dining area & grey oak laminate floors. Updates include new interior paint, bathroom mirrors, faucets, lighting fixtures in every part of the home, hardware, updated laundry room w/shelving, fencing & patio. Shy 1/4-acre lot makes for an expansive yard & includes a shed. RV parking, quiet cul-de-sac living yet close to town.

Discover comfort and convenience in this charming single-level 1-bed, 1-bath + office condo in Mount Vernon. Includes an attached 1-car garage, patio, and walk-in closet. Condo features new LVP floors throughout, ceiling fans, all new kitchen appliances + new washer/dryer, new gas furnace and garage opener. Perfect for modern living with updated amenities and a versatile office space large enough to be used as a spare bedroom. Located centrally for easy access to shops and parks. Ideal for down sizers seeking a low-maintenance lifestyle in a vibrant community 55 and older community with well maintained grounds and common space including community club house to host any events and socialize.

Situated on a large, level corner lot with great view of Mt Baker this fantastic, solidly built home has loads of character. This two bedroom 1 and 3/4 bath includes a large primary suite and attached bath. You'll enjoy the spacious loft and other bonus rooms needing only your imagination. Conveniently located just minutes from downtown, you'll love the vaulted ceilings and ample space this home provides. Plenty of parking with mature landscaping and, a metal roof this home is a must see!

Welcome to this home. Great opportunity to bring fresh new decorating ideas. This home has 3 bedrooms and an extra large family room. Primary bedroom with bathroom. Living room with a fireplace. Country style kitchen. Dining room opens up to an oversized deck. Utility room on lower level. Fenced back yard. Home could benefit with some updates. 2 car garage. Located close to city forest lands, pool and local schools.

Stunning westerly views over Padilla Bay and over to Fidalgo Island from this just under 2 1/2 acre property. Now is your chance to own a piece of this wonderful area of Bayview in Skagit Valley. Available in street are water and electricity, buyer to verify with county for specifics. Survey map complete and property markers in. Come build your dream home and a shop plus maybe an ADU above, or a getaway abode, grow a garden or have a greenhouse and enjoy life just outside the city. Within minutes from some of the best local restaurants and places in Bow, Edison, La Conner and more. Don't miss this opportunity.

Opportunity for an ample home with a garage, shop and RV parking in city limits! 3 bed/2.5 bath on its own fenced lot. Great floor plan with this bright open home with vaulted ceilings. Large master bedroom has walk-in closet and remodeled master bath with soaking tub and custom tiled shower. Both bathrooms have tiled flooring, new lighting and granite countertops. Ample kitchen with plenty of countertop space, solid oak cabinets, tile floor and skylights. Convenient desk space in the utility area and plenty of storage closets and extras throughout. Dont miss the RV parking, newer Hardi plank siding, AC and half bath out in the shop. Home comes with one year home warranty. NO HOA!

Desirable one level living in this charming 2 bedroom, 2 bath bungalow. Great in town location for easy access to local amenities. Spacious remodeled kitchen features quartz countertops, new cooktop/air fryer stove and newer fridge. Remodeled master bath with tiled shower and separate tub, quartz countertop with double sinks and heated floor. Private deck, patio and garden off of master bedroom. Custom front door. Beautifully landscaped yard with 2 decks for outdoor enjoyment. 1 car garage plus covered carport in addition to shop space, outdoor storage building and greenhouse. Newer siding is hand dipped cedar shakes. New electrical, plumbing & windows. Newer roof. This home has it all - just waiting for its new owners!

Welcome to Brickyard Park a 55+ community! This rambler plan features 3 bed 1.75 and is one of the most popular plans. This home has over $31K in upgrades. There is an open concept great room w/ a gas fireplace. The kitchen has upgraded cabinets, island & quartz countertops. Some of the upgrades include carpet, ADA toilets, upgraded interior doors & lights . Mini split for heat/cool. The primary suite bath has tile floor & tile shower. 2 car garage. There is a community clubhouse w/ an almost acre park w/a walking trail around it. There is a pickleball court, horseshoes & an area for lawn games. Covered rear patio. Fenced backyard. This is a premium lot!

Open Bright Floorplan nestled in a Serine well maintained community welcomes you home. Two car garage and entryway at street level and all living space on the second floor (primary, guest, + den/office/hobby room.) Recently added upgrades include heat pump with two ductless mini-split units providing ample efficient heat and cooling, luxury vinyl plank flooring, carpet and interior paint. Enjoy the privacy of the greenbelt behind this unit that this selected unit faces. Primary included dual closets, (one walk-in), and large bathroom with double sink vanity. Close and convenient to walking trails, parks, and amenities.

Embrace the allure of waterfront living on Fidalgo Island with southern exposure views of the bay and Whidbey Island. This beach cabin presents a unique opportunity to craft your ideal retreat with 122 feet of medium bank waterfront. Revel in the convenience of one-level living within this 1104 SF, 2 BD, 1.75 BA home, complemented by a detached garage and charming backyard retreat. Whether you're seeking a weekend escape or a year-round sanctuary, this property offers unrivaled potential. Just a scenic 90-minute drive from Seattle and Vancouver, immerse yourself in the serenity of this idyllic waterfront setting, conveniently close to Deception Pass bridge and NAS Whidbey. Don't miss your chance to make this dream a reality!

Experience luxury and carefree living in this upscale Eaglemont 3 story 3000+ sq ft condo! This END unit spans three levels but offers convenient one-level living. Freshly painted interiors with an updated kitchen complement the open living concept with vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, custom cabinetry, quartz counters, and two gas fireplaces. The primary suite features a spacious 5-piece bath. The lower level includes a spacious informal living room with built-in shelves and cozy fireplace, bonus room, media room, and a second primary suite. An office off the entry, a wrap-around deck, and a lower-level patio enhance the space. HOA dues cover exterior maintenance, landscaping, and exterior insurance. Don't miss this turnkey home!

Alexa, find me the perfect home! Alright. I've found it. Welcome to this meticulously kept single level home w/solar panels, generator, & smart home system allowing voice control throughout! Natural light fills the main living area up to the vaulted ceilings. Put your couch around the gas fireplace w/the TV mounted above. Kitchen has rich-toned wood cabinets, granite countertops & stainless-steel appliances. Primary bedroom is privately located opposite from two additional bedrooms/bathroom & has a walk-in closet & full bathroom equipped with a double vanity shower & tub. Outside is the front porch of your dreams, along w/a large front yard & fenced backyard w/patio, gazebo, fire pit, garden space, & more! Shall I dial your agent now?

Views to live for!!! The Summit at Rock Ridge offers amazing views in this desirable neighborhood in Anacortes. You will be proud to live in this beautiful neighborhood of Coastal Modern homes boasting panoramic views of the San Juan Islands and way beyond. Easy access to the Anacortes forest lands with trails to hike or bike. Anacortes Regional Airport and the San Juan Island ferries add to the fun of sitting on top of the world looking at this fabulous location.

Skyline home with unobstructed, panoramic, Salish Sea views. Cathedral ceilings and a wall of windows showcase the view from every room. Main level living in this 2, 113 sf home and 9 ceilings downstairs. Built for sustainability; solar panels, solar water heat, passive solar/convection, gas fireplaces, for big energy savings in this cozy home. The Mini-split heat pump system offers cooling too. Layered blinds and deck awning control heat on sunny days. Set on the lot for maximum view and privacy, adjacent to open greenspace. Impeccable condition move in ready. Fenced, southern exposure garden space and shaded lower patio with the same huge views. Comes with all Skyline amenities. Lots of storage space. Special features in supplements.

Nestled in the heart of old town Mt Vernon, this vintage craftsman home exudes timeless charm & character. Step into enchanting details like coved ceilings, pristine white millwork, & wood-wrapped windows. Living area features a cozy gas FP w/ a decorative surround. A chef's delight, updated kitchen boasts SS apps, granite counters, white subway tile w/ farmhouse-style apron sink & A WIP! Oversized primary bedroom w/ double doors to back yard, WIC & luxurious updated ensuite bath featuring dual sink vanity & walk-in shower. 2 add'l bedrooms & full bath provide ample space for guests. Relax in the fenced backyard oasis featuring a sizable detached storage shed, alongside a convenient carport. Upgrades: on demand H2O heater, heat pump A/C.

This manufactured home needs TLC but would make a great investment property or home for someone handy. A good option would be to remove the home and replace it with a new manufactured home. Skyline amenities offer beach access at Tugboat Park, Pickle ball/tennis at Skyline Park, Skyline club house, and a waterfront cabana for parties. Annual dues are $235.00. Home is being sold as is. This won't last long, so don't delay! WA Park and Skyline Marina are close by.

Step into serene living at Sedro Woolley's Premier 55+ Community! Nestled in a picturesque space, you'll be hard-pressed to find anything like it again. A modern residence, complete w/a cook's kitchen ideal for dining and casual meals at the peninsula; a generous and relaxing primary featuring an ensuite bathroom with a spacious shower, linen closet, and ample storage. Natural light abounds from numerous windows while offering views of lush green landscapes. Enjoy A/C and ceiling fans to enhance airflow and energy efficiency, providing comfort year-round. The Powered Oversized Shed makes the perfect space for hobbies & additional storage needs. Don't miss this rare opportunity to downsize to an affordable community in a tranquil environment

Looking for a place to get away? This very comfortable 480 sf cabin in the Cascade River Park. A gated for security, off grid community. This cabin was built in 2020 and also has a 160 sf covered porch, a large driveway for you and your friends with RV's to stay. A great open yard for lots of fun. The cabin has vaulted ceilings, sliding doors, nice appliances and fixtures, wood stove and propane heaters. The cabin is wired for a generator. There is lots of fire wood staked next to the porch. This is a great place to relax out side of the city. Lots of out door things to do. Fishing, hiking. exploring the Cascade forest. Come out and smell the fresh air, the smell of the forest and the campfire while you make good memories. Rentals are OK

Private retreat with incredible views of Skagit Bay & the Olympic Mountains from almost every room. Quality renovations and upgrades throughout this impressive home. Vaulted ceilings, skylights & oversized windows make this home feel open & spacious. Beautiful hardwood, bamboo & cork floors highlight clean lines & artistic details throughout. Relax on the 500sq.ft deck or in the renovated sunroom off the master bedroom and enjoy the nightly sunset show. Discover the walk-in jetted soaking tub, whole home generator & surge protector, XL5 Thermador cooktop & more! The lower level offers a fully functioning ADU with private entrance and patio. Enjoy all of Shelter Bay's many amenities: pickleball, tennis, pool, playground, marina & more.
